dataIdInfo.idPurp: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for the Northwestern Hawaiian Islands stock of false killer whales, which is largely within the Papahanaumokuakea Marine National Monument.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for the Northwestern Hawaiian Islands stock of false killer whales, which is largely within the Papahanaumokuakea Marine National Monument. This boundary is based on biological data as described in Bradford et al. (2015). More information on false killer whale stocks around the Hawaiian Islands can be found in the latest stock assessment report.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This shapefile was created by Amanda Bradford <amanda.bradford@noaa.gov> at the NOAA Fisheries Pacific Islands Fisheries Science Center. The current projection is WGS_1984_UTM_Zone_4N.
